<p>I have a working OAuth2RestTemplate client (I'm using spring-security-oauth2 2.0.7.RELEASE). Now I'd like to expose/wrap it as AsyncRestTemplate to take advantage of asynchronous semantic of ListenableFuture. Unfortunately the following straightforward approach doesn't work:</p>  <pre><code>// instantiate and configure OAuth2RestTemplate - works OAuth2RestTemplate oAuth2RestTemplate = new OAuth2RestTemplate(...);  // wrap sync restTemplate with AsyncRestTemplate - doesn't work  AsyncRestTemplate asyncRestTemplate = new AsyncRestTemplate(     new HttpComponentsAsyncClientHttpRequestFactory(), oAuth2RestTemplate); </code></pre>  <p>How can I get OAuth2 Rest client for my HTTP service as AsyncRestTemplate?</p>